snippet.title: Maharashtra Exit Poll | महाराष्ट्रात कुणाची बाजी? मविआ की महायुती? पाहा ग्राफिक्स N18EP
snippet.description:
The voting for the Lok Sabha Election 2024 was held a few days ago. The result will be announced on 4 June 2024. This general Lok Sabha election was held across the country. News18 network has conducted a mega exit poll on who will win this election. Voting in all the states, its geographical, social and other criteria have been studied. From this exit poll, it has been predicted how many seats all the parties including BJP, Congress, NCP, Shiv Sena will get, who will be elected where and who can be defeated.

जगातल्या सर्वात मोठ्या लोकशाहीची निवडणूक संपन्न झाली. सात टप्प्यात संपन्न झालेल्या या निवडणुकीत शेवटच मत पडताच आता प्रत्येकाच्या मनात  एकच प्रश्न आहे तो कुणाच्या हाती देशाची सत्ता येणार हा. श्वास रोखून संपूर्ण भारतातील जनता याची प्रतिक्षा करतेय. भारतातलं सर्वांत मोठं न्यूज नेटवर्क असलेलं न्यूज18 नेटवर्कनं भारतीय लोकशाहीच्या इतिहासात पहिल्यांदाच सर्व्हे घेऊन येतोय. आमचा हा EXIT नाही EXACT POLL आहे. 543 जागांवर जनतेनं काय फैसला यावर पाहा न्यूज18 नेटवर्कचा मेगा एक्झिट पोल पाहणार आहोत. 'न्यूज18 लोकमत'वर 'निकालाआधीचा निकाल' आम्ही तुम्हाला दाखवणार आहोत. सर्वात मोठा आणि विश्वसनीय 'एक्झिट पोल'मधून कुणाचं सरकार? जनतेनं कौल कुणाला दिला? कुणाच्या हाती देशाची सत्ता, पंतप्रधान कोण? कोणत्या पक्षाला किती जागा मिळणार? सर्व्हेत देशाचा विश्वास कुणावर? हे दाखवणार आहोत आम्ही 'न्यूज18 लोकमत'वर मेगा एक्झिट पोल'मध्ये. 


#News18ExitPoll #maharashtra  #exitpoll2024 #loksabhaelections2024

Stay updated on all the current events shaping Maharashtra's political landscape, with a special focus on key figures such as PM Narendra Modi, Amit Shah, Devendra Fadnavis, Ajit Pawar, Sharad Pawar, Eknath Shinde, Uddhav Thackeray, CMO Maharashtra, Aaditya Thackeray, Raj Thackeray, Manoj Jarange Patil, Prakash Ambedkar, and more.

snippet.title: Basirhat Lok Sabha Election 2024: Rekha Patra gets into heated argument with police in Sandeshkhali
snippet.description:
Basirhat Lok Sabha Election 2024: ভোটেও 'জ্বলল' সন্দেশখালি, 'গায়ে হাত দে, মেরে দেখা,' হুঁশিয়ারি রেখার। Rekha Patra gets into heated argument with police in Sandeshkhali Over the accusation that BJP supporters are being interrupted from voting. TMC slams her for allegedly creating disturbance in the area.

snippet.title: Sunday Brunch At Janhvi Kapoor's Bandra Home X Kamiya Jani | Ep 134 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be the first to catch all our videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

In this episode of Sunday Brunch, we had the pleasure of visiting Janhvi Kapoor's charming Bandra home for a delightful South Indian and North Indian fusion brunch. 

Fresh off the promotions for Mr. & Mrs. Mahi, Jhanvi quickly slipped into her comfy pajamas and laid out a feast that included dosa, idli, chicken curry, paneer bhurji, moong dal chilla, and much more. 

Jhanvi truly enjoyed the food with all her heart, more than any other celebrity guest we've had!

In this heartwarming episode, Jhanvi opens up about her acting journey, her special bond with her sister, childhood memories, her passion for food, and even shares relationship advice, highlighting the green and red flags she looks for in a boy, her film Mr. & Mrs. Mahi 

You'll get to see the relatable side of Jhanvi, whether as a homely individual, a foodie, or a caring elder sister, showing that she’s truly one of us.

We hope you enjoyed watching this video as much as we did making it.

Don’t forget to drop a comment on the quirkiest food combination Jhanvi suggested today, and it turned out to be surprisingly delicious!

snippet.description:
Dive into the uproarious world of reality TV with our latest comedy sketch, "A Day at the Reality Show Set"! 📺🤣
Join us for a behind-the-scenes tour that reveals the hilarious and chaotic reality of making reality shows. From the exaggerated drama to the off-camera antics, this sketch delivers a laugh-packed glimpse into the madness that viewers never get to see.
So, hit play and enjoy the comedic chaos of reality TV production like never before! 🎥😂 #RealityShowParody #BehindTheScenes

snippet.title: Exclusive Conversation With K Annamalai, As Exit Polls Point To BJP Debut In Tamil Nadu
snippet.description:
#kannamalai #bjp #tamilnadu #exitpolls2024 #exitpollwithbttv #loksabhaelections2024 
The India Today-Axis My India exit poll predicts a breakthrough for the BJP in Tamil Nadu with the saffron party expected to open its account in the state. Much of this is seen as the direct result of the efforts put in by K Annamalai, the BJP superstar in Tamil Nadu. The 39-year-old is contesting these elections from the crucial Coimbatore seat and is pitted against former mayor and DMK leader Ganapathi Raj Kumar. Here’s a special conversation with the young leader, a short while after the stunning India Today-Axis My India exit poll results were aired.

pt.title: Entrevista com Ruchi | Curta-metragem de comédia familiar | Ruchi e Piyush
pt.description:
Ruchi recebeu uma ligação de um repórter 😲
E eles querem entrevistar Ruchi🤩
Vamos ver o que acontece a seguir😉

snippet.title: Welcome to the Wild West! YEEHAW!
snippet.description:
Grab your cowboy hat and saddle up for an adventure! This season, the Wild West comes alive with exciting new challenges, an epic Super Wall Breaker Medal Event, rootin'-tootin' Hero skins and cosmetics, and much more. Yeehaw!


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: [HINDI] BGIS 2024 | WILDCARD | Day 2 | BGMI
snippet.description:
Welcome to WILDCARD ENTRY of the BGIS 2024! 

Prepare to be thrilled as 48 fierce teams from ROUND 04 and 16 contenders from ROUND 03 clash in the ultimate esports showdown! 🔥

BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024. It's a battlefield where legends #makewaves. With a whopping prize pool of INR 2 Crores, stakes are higher than ever.

Stay tuned! Witness emerging stars rise to fame and write their names in the BGIS history. Who will dominate? Who will surprise? Join us at 3:30 PM from Thursday to Sunday.


Don't forget to like, subscribe, and hit the notification bell to keep up with all the action. Your favourite players need your cheers, so drop your support in the comments below!


#MAKEWAVES  #BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIA  #INDIAKAGAME

Jaan Nisar Episode 11 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 1st June 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: GOAT SHIT | King & Karma | MM | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
#KING #Karma #GOATSHIT #MM

KING’s ‘GOAT SHIT’ serves as the mood-setting prelude to his highly anticipated project “MM” which has been teased over the past few months. Accompanied by Dehradun based rapper Karma, his latest single offers a glimpse into the narrative framework of his forthcoming project which pairs up his lyrical finesse and unbeatable flows with his fellow collaborator’s electrifying wordplay as the two brew up a storm with unapologetic confidence. Highlighted by a menacing production effort courtesy Delhi-based producer UKato, ‘GOAT SHIT’ stands out as an effortless showcase of KING and Karma’s no-holds barred approach.

Episode 4100: Abdul Ki Duty
--------------------------------------------------------
Abdul is busy running errands for the Gokuldham society members. Abdul's friend says that everyone is taking him for granted. Later, Bhide scolds Abdul for slacking off at his job.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4100 | 1 June 2024

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Jaan Nisar Episode 10 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 31st May 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.title: Praggnanandhaa stuns Magnus Carlsen | First win in Classical Chess | Norway Chess 2024
snippet.description:
Praggnanandhaa has beaten Magnus Carlsen several times before. This he managed to do in Champions Chess Tour in 2022. Recently at the Superbet Grand Chess Tour in Warsaw he beat Magnus for the first time in over the board chess, but that Blitz. Pragg had never beaten Carlsen in classical format. This he managed to do on 30th May 2024 at the 3rd round of the Norway Chess 2024. A fantastic game with tremendous accuracy. Check out this battle between the World no.1 and the rising star of Indian chess with commentary by IM Sagar Shah.

Video: ChessBase India

snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4099: Jethalal Scolds Abdul
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak urgently calls everyone to his house, announcing that Anjali has made juice for everyone to taste. Everyone tries to make excuses to avoid it. Later, Abdul gets scolded by Jethalal and Champaklal in front of his friend.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4099 | 31 May 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000277123

snippet.title: Dekhha Tenu - Lyric Video| Mr.&Mrs. Mahi |Rajkummar,Janhvi|Mohd. Faiz|Jaani
snippet.description:
The love anthem of the year is here!

Presenting the lyric video of the timeless love song ‘Dekhha Tenu’ from the film ‘Mr. and Mrs. Mahi’ - out now! Starring the lead cast – Janhvi Kapoor and Rajkummar Rao in the video, the video depicts their love story in the movie. With the original song ‘Say Shava Shava’ composed by Aadesh Shrivastava and penned by Sameer Anjaan, the new version is composed and written by Jaani. Sung in the captivating voice of Mohammad Faiz, this song is a magnificent treat to the ears.

snippet.title: Pandharpur Vitthal Temple Basement Found | हीच का 'ती' मूळ मुर्ती? काय सांगतायेत अभ्यासक?
snippet.description:
In the basement of Vitthal Temple of Pandharpur, however, the officials of the department directly entered and inspected. After this some idols have been found in this cellar seven to eight different types of stone idols, coins have now been brought out from the cellar. Assistant Director of Archeology Department Vilas Vahane is currently inspecting and studying the idols. The possibility of some new remains coming out of this basement is now being expressed.

पंढरपूरच्या विठ्ठल मंदिरातील तळघरात परंतु विभागाच्या अधिकाऱ्यांनी थेट प्रवेश करून पाहणी केली. यानंतर या तळघरात काही मुर्त्या आढळून आले आहेत सात ते आठ प्रकारच्या वेगवेगळ्या दगडी मुर्त्या,  नाणी हे आता तळघरातून बाहेर काढण्यात आले आहे. याबाबत पुरातत्व विभागाचे सहाय्यक संचालक विलास वाहने हे सध्या मुर्त्यांची पाहणी करून अभ्यास करत आहेत. या तळघरातून अजूनही काही नवे अवशेष बाहेर येण्याची शक्यता आता व्यक्त होत आहे. 

#vitthal #vitthalmandir #pandharpur #marathinews #news18lokmat

snippet.description:
Welcome to our channel! Beat the heat and tantalize your taste buds with our easy homemade nimbu pani recipe! In this video, we'll guide you through the simple steps to create the perfect balance of tangy lemons, sweetness, and a hint of spice, resulting in the ultimate thirst-quenching beverage.

Whether you're lounging in your backyard, hosting a summer party, or simply craving a refreshing drink, nimbu pani is the answer. Join us as we show you how to transform basic ingredients into a rejuvenating drink that's bursting with flavor and goodness.

FOLLOW KARLO 😘
Instagram :  https://www.instagram.com/yash.ke.experiments/ 
Facebook :  https://www.facebook.com/yashkexperiments

Our nimbu pani recipe requires just a few ingredients that you likely already have in your kitchen. From fresh lemons to sugar, salt, and water, we'll walk you through each step of the process, ensuring that you achieve the ideal blend of flavors every time.

But wait, there's more! We'll also share some tips and tricks to customize your nimbu pani to suit your taste preferences. Whether you prefer it extra tangy, lightly sweetened, or infused with herbs, we've got you covered.

So, what are you waiting for? Grab your ingredients and let's get started on this refreshing culinary adventure together! Don't forget to like, share, and subscribe for more delicious recipes and tips. Cheers to homemade nimbu pani!

snippet.title: Al Hilal 1 - 1 Al Nassr (5 - 4 Penalties) | Final | Highlights | King's Cup | 31st May 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/football-king-s-cup-1700001359

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

Al Hilal triumphed over Al Nassr to win the King's Cup in a sizzling match that extended to a penalty shootout. Both teams were evenly matched during regular and extra time, resulting in a tie that was ultimately decided by the tiebreaker, where Al Hilal emerged victorious. The fans witnessed a thrilling final but Cristiano Ronaldo had a heartbreak yet again.
